 to remember - we went once or twice to a London theatre. That would be after 19 - after that nine months at Stony Stratford that I told you - when we did get a house in Guildford - we used to go sometimes to a London}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid11808836\charrsid6631206  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 theatre and give ourselves an evening out - yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15540585 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Did you ever go to a concert of music-hall?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8652529 AP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Er - well, in London once or twice - yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15540585 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Cinemas?
