place to myself was that - yes - which was the main thing. And home decorating I was - I got to be very good at the indoor decorating yes., yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15540585 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Before the do-it-yourself age?
