No. My wife doesn't like cats - she can't bear them - she's one of these people who can't bear a cat in the room and - we've never had a dog.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15540585 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Did your wife ever go out to enjoy herself? On her own.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8652529 AP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 
Er - no. Not really. I think when we did set up home in Guildford - occasionally a neighbour who was friendly with her - they'd go off together somewhere - yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15540585 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Did anyone outside the home help your wife to look after her house and family?
