Oh yes. When we first set up in Guildford - a neighbour who was quite anxious to earn a little money - she used to come in and do a bit of housework for my wife - yes, yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15540585 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 And that would be a friend really?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8652529 AP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Er - really, yes, but not terribly friendly - she was a little bit -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15540585 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 A neighbour?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8652529 AP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Yes, that's it and - er - not very imaginative I remember - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15540585 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 That would be regularly?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8652529 AP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Oh yes, she used to come in two or three mornings a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15540585 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 If your wife was confined to bed how did you manage?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8652529 AP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Well, it was a matter of doing the best we could. This - woman would come in a little - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15540585 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Did either of you have any relatives living nearby?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8652529 AP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Yes - my mother was in Guildford here, you see, and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15540585 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Did you see much of her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8652529 AP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Oh yes. She used to come up occasionally and we used to run down there and see them occasionally - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15540585 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Of course your sister had gone north?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8652529 AP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Gone away and - we never saw any more of her - yers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15540585 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Did your mother come to see you in your home or did you always go to see her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8652529 AP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Oh no. She used to come up there and give my wife a little advice on some things or other which wasn't always taken.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15540585 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Did you have any friends? Did you make friends in Guildford?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8652529 AP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 
Oh yes. Going up in the train I met one or two people I got to know very well - and as a matter of fact I - I joined the - Wesleyian they called them in those days - I joined their gym - gymnasium - yes, and we had some jolly times there - y
es - every winter for several winters used to go.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15540585 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 So you would see them at this club?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8652529 AP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 That's right - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15540585 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 And also on the train?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8652529 AP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 On the train.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15540585 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Did you share the same friends - you and your wife?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8652529 AP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Well, yes, she'd be friendly with - one particular one I remember - the wife was very friendly with my wife and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15540585 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Did you both have some friends that the other didn't share?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8652529 AP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Not, really that I can think of - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15540585 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 For instance she might not know all the people you met on the train?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8652529 AP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Oh no, she wouldn't know all those - no, no, that's right - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15540585 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Perhaps there might be people she went out with in Guildford that you didn't know?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8652529 AP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Not very much - no, she was not - quite a home bird she was - yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15540585 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Were friends invited into your home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8652529 AP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Oh yes. The friends that we knew just round about, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15540585 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Often?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8652529 AP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Not often, no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15540585 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Would they be offered anything to eat or drink?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8652529 AP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Oh yes. They'd come in perhaps - it was a great thing to go to tea with each other - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15540585 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 And would there be any particular day or occasion?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8652529 AP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Oh no. No particular - just as it happened - odd .....
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15540585 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 And would they be your wife's friends or the friends you shared?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8652529 AP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Well, generally speaking, my wife's friends I think - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15540585 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Did people sometimes call in casually without an invitation?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8652529 AP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Oh yes. That would happen occasionally - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15540585 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 And would neighbours do the same?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8652529 AP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Oh yes, I think a bit - yes - not much though - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15540585 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 How much did you go out to visit friends and neighbours?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8652529 AP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Not much - no - not very frequently - very infrequently really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15540585 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 People often tell us that in those days they made their own amusements - what did you do when you got together with friends or neig
hbours? Did you have music or games?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8652529 AP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 
There would be a little - we had a piano in those days I remember and there would be a little playing - I was no pianist - my wife just a little - but sometimes a friend would know more about it than - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15540585 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 You might have a sing-song?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8652529 AP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Just a little one - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15540585 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Would you play any games?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8652529 AP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 No, I wouldn't like to say that we did somehow - no - never ......
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15540585 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Sit and talk?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8652529 AP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Talk. It would be chatter - yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15540585 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Was your home rented?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8652529 AP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Yes, in those days it was - yes. That was the only way to get one - yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15540585 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Did you see anything of your landlord?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8652529 AP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Well, no - it was a - a council housing estate, so the landlord was sort of indefinite somebody.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15540585 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 In the area where you lived then who were considered the most important people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8652529 AP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 
Well, we were all much about the same sort of people I think - yes. A very mixed crowd as a matter of fact - quite labouring people some of them, you know, I'm not despising that at all but - they were quite a lot - very mixed indeed - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15540585 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 But others would be different?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8652529 AP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Different - yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15540585 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 In what sort of way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8652529 AP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Well, more skilled and - quite a number with similar jobs in a bank or something of that sort you know and a few 
Civil Servants and things of that sort.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15540585 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 
So would you think perhaps that the group that you belonged to was the more educated group in that community would be their ore important group?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8652529 AP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 More important in a way - yes - but I can never look down on people - I can never
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15540585 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Would they look up to you?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8652529 AP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 A little bit perhaps - just a little - yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15540585 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Was this because they had a better job and had more money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8652529 AP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Well, that had a lot to do with it I think, yes, yes. You made a better impression with your garden and things like that you see - yes.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15540585 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 What about the shopkeepers who did they associate with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8652529 AP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Now you've beaten me there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15540585 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Did you know any?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8652529 AP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 I didn't - can't think in those days - I didn't know any really not - no I didn't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15540585 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 You had a grocer friend?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8652529 AP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Ah - yes, that was away in 1919 - after - after I came out - yes, well .....
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15540585 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Who would he be friendly with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8652529 AP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Well, he was a great man in the Congregational church at Stony Stratford - oh yes, yes, yes. And we used to go there because of that - yes.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15540585 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 What about the clergy - did you come in contact with the clergy at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8652529 AP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 I didn't - no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15540585 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 You don't know what sort of group they mixed with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8652529 AP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Er - I can't say because I didn't know any
, you see, because this Congregational group I only just knew my friend and just one or two people I met at sort of little - extra meetings they had and things like that but I - I never met their Minister for instance or anything like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15540585 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Coming back to Guildford - did you know any teachers when you were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1060851 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8652529 AP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Well, I'd forgotten all about teachers and things like that by that time, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15540585 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 I wondered if you had any as friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8652529 AP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 No, I didn't remember - no, no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15540585 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Would you remember who they would associate with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8652529 AP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Well, I wouldn't know anything about them really. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15540585 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Did you come across any farmers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8652529 AP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Only in my holidays - yes. As a boy and onwards - and even after we came back from the war - down in Berkshire - yes, 
yes. But they were not farmers on their own - they were tenant farmers you see, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15540585 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 What about employers - did you know any employers and who they associated with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8652529 AP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 No, I can't say that I did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15540585 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 What sort of people would you say went to church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8652529 AP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Er - well, quite a mixed Congregationist - mixture really I remember -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15540585 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 This is after you were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1060851 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 ?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8652529 AP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Yes
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8652529 AP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 There was quite a little group of all sorts that went along to our little church in Onslow village when it was formed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15540585 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 You went to a church in Onslow Village?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8652529 AP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 When I - we came back here in 19 - 1921 that would be when we finally came here and set up home in Guildford - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15540585 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 And there was quite a mixed group?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8652529 AP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Quite a mixed group - yes, all sorts.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15540585 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 What about the chapel? To the Congregational - Wesleyian - Methodist? Did you know any?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8652529 AP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 No, I used to go to their gymnasium but that was my only connection with them - yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15540585 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Did you have friends that went there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8652529 AP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Er - can't recollect any. 
Except that when we lived in 1921 some friends of ours one of the friends that we spoke about just now they used to go to the Congregational - er - Wesleyian church - yes. But I don't know much about their doings or how they got on or ......
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15540585 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Or what sort of people went to it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8652529 AP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15540585 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 
Where you lived here in Onslow Village - did all the people in the working class have the same standard of living or would you say there were different groups?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8652529 AP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Well, rather different groups I think - Onslow Vi
llage is a bit - it had a reputation for being a bit uppish you see - thought they were a bit better than most you see - yes, in fact it showed up at All Saints Church. When we first started to go there - there were the Guildford Park people - which was t
he housing estate you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15540585 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Would that be working class?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8652529 AP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 
Yes, most of them by that time - other people like - lots of people had moved out to Onslow Village and similar sorts of places - and - so All Saints Church when it first started so far as I
 recollect - the Onslow Village people and the - Guildford Park people sat on opposite sides of the church and they didn't easily mix - no - and that - well, that was quite notable - noticed - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15540585 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 What sort of family would be in the - if it was a wor
king class family in the Guildford Park group - what sort of a family would be the Onslow Village group? How would you describe the difference - would it be the same sort of thing you mentioned before about having more education?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8652529 AP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 More education - yes
 - and better jobs - yes. Travellers and - bank clerks and that kind of thing - yes - and people who went up - a lot of people went up to London - yes, oh yes, quite a big crowd - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15540585 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Were some families thought of as rough and some as respectable?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8652529 AP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 
I can't say that that was so with Onslow, Village - no. But it was definitely so in the housing estate - in the - in Guildford Park - oh quite definitely - yes. In fact we had to get the police on one occasion to - we got our garden - the delphiniums a
nd things like that were term up you see and I remember a detective came along and }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2633972\charrsid6631206 hid}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 
 himself and watched - but he - he never caught anybody but still it was a bit troublesome - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15540585 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 What would people feel about this sort of thing - would it make the local people angry?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8652529 AP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Yes - it was - spoken to be as jealously.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15540585 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Would they know who had done it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8652529 AP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 
Well, we had a suspicion that our neighbours - the one that used to come and help my wife - I think she knew who it was - yes - but she never gave away - gave the game away - no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15540585 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 So nobody was accused of doing this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8652529 AP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 
Oh no. But having known that we'd got the police sort of having a look around and that kind of thing - it stopped. Yes. But that is the kind of thing that was likely to happen up there somehow.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15540585 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Would there be a distinction of rough an}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2633972\charrsid6631206 d respectable between craftsmen}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206  and labourers? Would it be that sort of distinction or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8652529 AP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Well, I suppose so in a way - yes. The rough ones were really rough., you know, their 
jobs were poor and labouring - definitely labouring jobs - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15540585 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 So the Onslow Village group might have felt itself superior?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8652529 AP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Well, they did so - yes, yes. I can't say that I took part in that because I'm a great leveler myself - I'm friends with everybody almost.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15540585 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Did you have a struggle to make ends meet at that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8652529 AP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 
Oh quite a lot - yes - because my wife was in poor health and in fact we've had a doctor all the time - yes - and nowadays - even now my wife's on his private list Doctor
 Mercer's list, you see, not that he has to see her very much but he said it's better for her to stay like that because she'd never go to his surgery and when he does come he sits and has a long chat with her - to do her good and that kind of thing - yes.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15540585 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 What did you feel about it at the time - do you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8652529 AP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Not unduly worried - I'm a great optimist really - yes - we always thought we'd pull through and we did - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15540585 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 What difference did it make if you were ill or out of work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8652529 AP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Never out of work and fortunately I was never ill - no. Yes, very fortunate - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15540585 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Did you ever get any help from the Parish or a charity?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8652529 AP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Oh no, no, no. My daughter for instance, one - qualified for scholarships but because the Civil Service pay - n
ot very wonderful but it was above the limit and so we had to pay for her - from beginning to end you see at the Country school - Country Grammar School - yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15540585 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 What was your job when you finished at Somerset House - what were you doing towards the end of your career?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8652529 AP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Well, it was an accounts job - yes. Accounting - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15540585 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 How would you describe it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8652529 AP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Well, it's nearly just - putting all the receipts into various categories and somebody - got to be all analysed and the treasury - make 
a report to the treasury how much we'd got under various headings and all that kind of thing you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15540585 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 What would you be officially called?
\par }\pard\plain \ltrpar\s15\qj \fi-461\li461\ri0\sa240\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin461\itap0\pararsid15540585 \rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs24\alang1025 \ltrch\fcs0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8652529 AP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid349627\charrsid6631206 Well, I finished up - when did you mean? When I retired I was a Higher Executive Officer. Yes, yes. Yes, yes.
\par }}